{% extends '../_home.twig' %}
{% block titletag %}About
{% endblock %}
{% block bodytag %}

	<main class="Site-content">
	<section class="about">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-12">
					<h2 class="main-heading">About</h2>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-4 col-xs-mobile">
					<div class="about-picture">
							<img class="img-fluid" src="{{img}}/about/about-me.jpg" alt="about-me">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-xs-8 col-xs-mobile">
					<div class="about-details">
						<p>
							I’m an independent UI/UX Designer based in Ludhiana, Punjab. I love the Web and mobile platform and I want to make it better for everyone.
						</p>
						<p>
							I have a Bachelor’s Degree in Computer Science and Master Degree in M.B.A (information Technology). But everything I know of Web today is self-taught and knowledge that i acquire while working in different organisations.
						</p>
						<p>
						I have 5+ years of experience. In these years i work on various projects.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row mt-xs-50">
				<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-xs-8 col-xs-mobile">
					<div class="about-details">
						<h2>Hobbies</h2>
						<p>
							Apart from working, I have passion for filmaking. So to pursue this I started making Vlogs to learn about the various aspects of it. Here is link to my youtube channel. Apart from this I have started reading books from last 2-3 years to get some wisdom and improve my productivity. Last book that I read was Atomic Habits by James clear
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-4 col-xs-mobile">
					<div class="about-picture">
						<img class="img-fluid" src="{{img}}/about/hobbies.jpg" alt="hobbies">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	</main>

{% endblock %}
